QShowDiff
==========
Tool for visualisation of diffs generated from various VCS systems.


Requirements
-------------
For compilation you need only Qt4 devel files.


Compilation and Installation
----------------------------
For compilation just type:
    make
If you want to change default type of parsed diff (git) you can specify it
by setting variable DEFAULT_TYPE in make command. For example:
    make DEFAULT_TYPE=svn

For installation to /usr/local/bin type:
    sudo make install
And if you want to change destination dir:
    sudo make DESTDIR=/path/to/dir install

